name: Just ask me out
tag_list: online-dating, dating-website, dating-site, dating-agency, dating-agencies, personals
overview:
Justaskmeout is a new type of dating site that is all about just asking people out and meeting up, so that members can spend their precious time on dates, not on lengthy messaging and winks etc.

The idea is simple: If you like someone, you just ask them out. The site provides you with great date ideas for you to pick from, or you can suggest your own.

We are just focusing on launching in London and the surrounding areas initially with a view to expanding beyond that soon.

Justaskmeout plans to revolutionise the way people use online dating by getting people offline, on real-life dates as quickly as possible.
